<author>rwbrt mwrys, bhjt ʿdly, Robert Morris</author>
<hymn_number>5244</hymn_number>
<title>qṣd ạltjsd ạlʿẓym</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qaṣ̊du ạltãjasũdi ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 ḥas̊ba masẖūrāti ạlạảzal̊
 ạảʿ̊lanahu ạl̊fādī ạl̊karīm̊
 ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlībi kāl̊ḥamal̊

[V2]
 2- ại̹nãhu ạảkẖ̊lay̱ naf̊sahu
 wāảkẖadẖa maqāmanā
 wāllhu qad̊ ḍarabahu
 bisaẙfihi lạảj̊linā

[V3]
 3- lamãạ rāảy̱ ạlsãẙfa ạl̊tahab̊
 qad̊ ṣāḥa min̊ haẘli ạl̊gẖaḍab̊
 &quot;ại̹ylī lima tarak̊tanī
 wawaj̊huka ʿanĩy ạḥ̊tajab̊?&quot;

[V4]
 4- &quot;ại̹nãka qad̊ ḍarab̊tanī
 bisaẙfi ʿad̊lika ạlrãhīb̊&quot;
 &quot;qad̊ dẖāba qal̊bī dākẖilī
 kālsẖãm̊ʿi ạảmāma ạllãhīb̊&quot;

[V5]
 5- nakãsa rā̊̉sahu ạl̊karīm̊
 wamāta ʿanãạ dẖā ạl̊ḥanūn̊
 muḥ̊tamilạaⁿ kulã ạl̊gẖaḍab̊
 wadẖāyỉqaⁿạ haẘla ạl̊manūn̊

[V6]
 6- fī jul̊jutẖā rabĩy qaḍay̱
 ʿanĩy ʿalay̱ ʿūdi ạlṣãlīb̊
 fī jul̊jutẖā nil̊tu ạlrĩḍay̱
 fālsẖũk̊ru lil̊fādī ạl̊ḥabīb̊</lyrics>
</song>